data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET - at NO fault to seller.  Buyer's loan did not go through. Discover your dream home at 13824 Gavina Avenue in Sylmar! This stunning eco-friendly residence boasts 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, encompassing 1,316 square feet of living space on a generous 9,348 square foot lot with an attached 2-car garage. As you enter, the well-thought-out floor plan, complemented by laminate floors, recessed lighting, and an abundance of natural light, will immediately captivate you. The spacious living room, adorned with a cozy fireplace, sets the perfect atmosphere for unwinding and enjoying moments with friends and family. Adjacent to the living room, you'll find the dining area and a chef’s kitchen equipped with modern appliances, a double sink, and ample storage and counterspace. Featuring 4 well-proportioned bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home ensures comfort and convenience. Outside, a spacious patio with a covered area awaits, providing the ideal space for outdoor cooking and entertaining. Noteworthy features include vaulted ceilings, Nest, a smart lock, a smart-controlled recessed lighting system, newer HVAC and windows, a tankless water heater, Tesla charger in garage, prewire for ADT alarm system, exterior cameras, and owned solar panels with a Tesla Powerwall. Buyer to assume the solar panel and power wall agreements. Centrally located in Sylmar, this home enjoys proximity to schools, parks, shopping, dining, and more. Don't miss the opportunity to make this eco-friendly oasis your own. Call us today for a showing!
